articles.title: Reserves added as Australia finalise squad for T20 World Cup - ICC Cricket
articles.description: Australia have locked in their final squad for the ICC Men's T20 World Cup 2024, confirming their 15-player group and travelling reserves.
articles.content:
Australia open their T20 World Cup campaign against Oman in Barbados on June 5, before Group B fixtures against England, Namibia and Scotland.
